OL,5, French car manufacturer Citroen has    
OL,6, been accused of normalising sexual     
OL,7, harassment in an advertisement in Egypt
OL,8, that features the pop star Amr Diab.   
OL,10,FIn the video, Diab uses a camera on his
OL,11,Fcar to photograph a woman crossing the 
OL,12,Froad, apparently without her consent.  
OL,13,FThey are later seen driving together.  
OL,15,FThe advert was released on 3 December  
OL,16,Fbut it has been criticised on social   
OL,17,Fmedia in recent days.                  
OL,19,FThe Egyptian-American journalist Reem  
OL,20,FAbdellatif described it as "creepy".   
